{"tid":1817954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾透露深圳被捕　王婆婆：離開「小籠」仍身處「大籠」　我可以輸但你一定要贏","createTime":"2020-01-09T13:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T04:02:11.000Z","uid":8968,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"28679d88e1b25951789432aa9f3c34fb5f20c244","tid":1817954,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Baq6gK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Baq6gK.png&h=c83eaf59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在反修例運動早前集會中，經常在抗爭現場揮舞港英旗的「王婆婆」王鳳瑤，自今年 8 月 11 日在太古港鐵站被帶走後不知去向，其後在 11 月底《立場新聞》收到王婆婆訊息，她透露自己正在深圳被捕後取保候審。《立場》記者今天再收到王婆婆的電郵，她用英文指自己雖然從「小籠（small cage）」被釋放，但現時身處「大籠（）big cage」，她又表示自己每天以淚洗面，字裡行間亦類似曾提出回港就醫，但都回覆無期。<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆在電郵中，勉勵港人：「我可以輸，但是，你一定要贏！！！」她的電郵亦透露更多被拘禁的細節，例如在去年 8 月 14 日被送入福田拘留所，罪名是「尋釁滋事罪」，然後 8 月 30 日被轉到深圳市第三看守所，她形容為「地獄」。<br />\n<br />\n福田拘留所應為福田看守所，位於深圳市福田區梅觀路8號，主要關押被判處有期徒刑一年以下，或者餘下刑期在一年以下，不便送往勞動改造場所執行的罪犯，也可以由看守所監管。至於深圳市第三看守所，位於福田區上梅林梅村路預審監管支隊大院內，和福田拘留所相隔約 2 公里路。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上資料指，深圳市第三看守所主要關押外國籍犯罪嫌疑人、重大經濟犯罪嫌疑人和職務犯罪嫌疑人，並設有深圳市女子專門監區。<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆電郵全文：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHello! My Friend,<br />\n<br />\nI am still alive without soul!<br />\nHave been released from the small cage.<br />\nNow!!!<br />\nBe inside the big cage!!!<br />\nThe sky is so grey.<br />\nI cry everyday,<br />\nhave been prohibited to have Known and My-say.<br />\nTrying to fly the way back to<br />\nzzzzz ......ffffly..fly ..Zzz nineteen ninety-ZZseven.<br />\n<br />\n您好！！！<br />\n<br />\n2019我輸----<br />\n8.11 在港被&lsquo;狂&rsquo;暴警打傷入院<br />\n8.14 一生正直無私，卻於&lsquo;心顫&rsquo;無辜入獄（福田拘留所, 尋釁滋事罪）<br />\n8.30 轉入地獄（深圳市第三看守所）<br />\n9.29 假出獄<br />\n9.29-10.03 愛國教育！！學&lsquo;酒'肉(走肉）,<br />\n之後，習&lsquo;行C&rsquo;，<br />\n變無知！！！<br />\n至今....<br />\n<br />\n回港求醫？？？<br />\n等到呆呆癡癡！！！（嗚哇！嗚哇！！嗚....）<br />\n<br />\n我可以輸，<br />\n但是，你一定要贏！！！<br />\n送&lsquo;講&rsquo;豬，<br />\n送淚雨。<br />\n迎金鼠，<br />\n贏真（人）民（作）主！！！<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆（Alexandra Wong）敬上 Shenzhen, 2020.01.09"},{"pid":"7b457e34703bb50fee2aaf082d924c273c317763","tid":1817954,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fc114261ae11d55020ddaf867005e3ebe67f34","tid":1817954,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"王婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd231226a6f915bbf9e42755c6979d27e6aec42a","tid":1817954,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44fc114261ae11d55020ddaf867005e3ebe67f34","tid":1817954,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"王婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"希望真係冇事🙏🏻"},{"pid":"93cb77ee86743991d51dbe66909de8e00bf021f9","tid":1817954,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4883fe407ecad4b04d99442fc06a728569915cb6","tid":1817954,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"一定要贏呀 聽到未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b7f93cccf4cb3451cdb59b2bcf9564bb9cfe90","tid":1817954,"uid":331173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"唔L係下化，係唔係克警押咗佢上大陸？"},{"pid":"9b3bdf33baa6a511da258bc84a90d58faed8cb7d","tid":1817954,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"好似鄭文傑咁? 可能仲金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3862e946ff3ad52e12eca1127d63c0dcc9fe474c","tid":1817954,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c082b0317421ccb422869b3f1c5f7fb32ac88ac1","tid":1817954,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:40:18.000Z","msg":"王婆婆其實咩background <br />\n英文咁好<br />\n唔應該住深圳"},{"pid":"eaa8ac2bd15a2ac1f4a834f4a98cfe4b8ea94d9e","tid":1817954,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"行動前思考三大重點：目的，可行性，後果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1818296\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1818296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b922da723b09f0b96d064a3e51c5ce98c4c91fda","tid":1817954,"uid":259860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d2a82ed3f5b37f2e40202b9981ffc6902dd022","tid":1817954,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"香港人可以反抗未?"},{"pid":"2ba8fd3091dd58f90e673540e3c9a232ac3650e9","tid":1817954,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"只要你係中國有物業，中國政府就夾你入境，話你自願去中國時被捕"},{"pid":"e1896be0ffc72bba85dd2103e